INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3505, 1, '2016-02-15 10:32:25', '2016-02-15 10:32:25', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bottom_padding="30"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1455064842096{background-color: #e2e4c5 !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]<span style="color: #4d5961;">At YES FS we have a unique service that sets us apart from our competitors and is offered exclusively to our clients. This service was designed to be innovative, creative and thinking outside the square. It has been thoroughly researched and has produced superior results. Our determination is backed by a wide range of specific financials skills, business acumen and experience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">Your personal situation and budget requirements change as you navigate your way through life. You may be unsure whether your current financial situation will suit your ongoing requirements, or your lifestyle simply may not permit you to continue your current strategy. Perhaps you just want a second opinion. We pride ourselves in taking care of our service to you and this will always be delivered to highest standards.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">We believe in the value of property and our expertise in this area differentiates us from other service providers who claim to educate and are a conduit to specialists. Our strategic relationship with property owners allows us to provide a unique service. We offer clients the opportunity to acquire property directly from property owners and benefit from not having to pay commission to real estate agents. Purchasing property is one of the most important decisions that you will have to make and it is a comfort to know that we can assist you through this process.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="3381" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left" css=".vc_custom_1455061958870{margin-top: 25px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][block_title inner_style_title="only_text" title="Who we are"]Learn more about our company and our history[/block_title][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1455064833832{background-color: #e2e4c5 !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]<span style="color: #4d5961;">The Managing Director of Yes FS holds a Master of Finance from RMIT and Certificate IV in Mortgage Broking. He has been involved in the financial services industry for more than a decade in a number of different roles ranging from executive director, consultant, senior financial planner, strategic advisor to managed funds, and Australian Financial Services Licence holder. He also owns multiple investment properties.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">He is a board member of the Diane Cilento Foundation, and a member of the Australian Institute of Company Directors.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">The Lending Manager has been working in the finance industry for more than 10 years. During that time he has gained valuable experience in structuring finance for a number of clients in residential &amp; commercial lending and equipment leasing. Brendon is accredited with over 30 lenders, holds top professional membership category with the Finance Brokers Association of Australia (FBAA) and is licenced by ASIC to provide credit assistance.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1455061572552{margin-top: 25px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="3380" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1538-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 10:32:25', '2016-02-15 10:32:25', '', 1538, 'http://localhost/yesfs/index.php/2016/02/15/1538-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
