INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3731, 1, '2016-02-26 14:35:54', '2016-02-26 14:35:54', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bottom_padding="30"][vc_column][block_title inner_style_title="only_text" title="Who we are"]Learn more about our company and our history[/block_title][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1455532414657{background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]<span style="color: #4d5961;">At YES FS we have a unique service that sets us apart from our competitors and is offered exclusively to our clients. This service was designed to be innovative, creative and thinking outside the square. It has been thoroughly researched and has produced superior results. Our determination is backed by a wide range of specific financials skills, business acumen and experience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">Your personal situation and budget requirements change as you navigate your way through life. You may be unsure whether your current financial situation will suit your ongoing requirements, or your lifestyle simply may not permit you to continue your current strategy. Perhaps you just want a second opinion. We pride ourselves in taking care of our service to you and this will always be delivered to highest standards.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">We believe in the value of property and our expertise in this area differentiates us from other service providers who claim to educate and are a conduit to specialists. Our strategic relationship with property owners allows us to provide a unique service. We offer clients the opportunity to acquire property directly from property owners and benefit from not having to pay commission to real estate agents. Purchasing property is one of the most important decisions that you will have to make and it is a comfort to know that we can assist you through this process.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1455532518243{background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]<span style="color: #4d5961;">The Managing Director of Yes FS holds a Master of Finance from RMIT and Certificate IV in Mortgage Broking. He has been involved in the financial services industry for more than a decade in a number of different roles ranging from executive director, consultant, senior financial planner, strategic advisor to managed funds, and Australian Financial Services Licence holder. He also owns multiple investment properties.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">He is a board member of the Diane Cilento Foundation, and a member of the Australian Institute of Company Directors.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">The Lending Manager has been working in the finance industry for more than 10 years. During that time he has gained valuable experience in structuring finance for a number of clients in residential &amp; commercial lending and equipment leasing. Brendon is accredited with over 30 lenders, holds top professional membership category with the Finance Brokers Association of Australia (FBAA) and is licenced by ASIC to provide credit assistance.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1455061572552{margin-top: 25px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="3730" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="right-to-left"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1538-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-26 14:35:54', '2016-02-26 14:35:54', '', 1538, 'http://localhost/yesfs/index.php/2016/02/26/1538-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3732, 1, '2016-02-26 14:38:06', '2016-02-26 14:38:06', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" bg_color="#f8f8f8"][vc_column][block_title title="Our Services"][/block_title][vc_column_text]Now is the perfect time to refinance your home loan. The competition between the banks is heating up and all refinance related break fees have been abolished by the Federal Government so the time is right to consider the various options and benefits available to you by refinancing.\r\n\r\nAn Outsource Financial Specialist will take the time to evaluate your current situation and make the appropriate recommendations in terms of your loan structure. Known as our ‘Accelerated Debt Reduction’ program this structure provides you with the necessary financial tools to repay your home loan as quickly as possible.\r\n\r\nWe will also ensure if you have any investment loans that they are structured in the most tax effective manner, allowing you to take advantage of any potential tax benefits that your current loan structure does not allow.\r\n\r\nFinance services are provided by our <strong>Authorised Credit Representative (ACR 446716)</strong>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type="full_width_background" top_padding="0"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="25px"][vc_tabs][vc_tab title="Fast cash" tab_id="1455585595655-6-8"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]We have no data here as well![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Refinancing" tab_id="1426935954367-8"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Today’s competitive home lending market makes refinancing much easier than in the past. There are many good reasons to consider refinancing. Perhaps your financial circumstances have changed, you’ve started a new job or are dissatisfied with your existing lender. Maybe your current mortgage no longer suits your needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>When to switch</strong>\r\nSwitching loans or lenders (or both) could be the answer. But it can also be risky. To assess if you’re likely to benefit from refinancing, ask yourself:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n	<li>am I happy with my lender?</li>\r\n	<li>do I need reduced or added features with my loan?</li>\r\n	<li>am I paying too many bank fees?</li>\r\n	<li>is the interest rate too high?</li>\r\n	<li>have my financial circumstances changed?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Refinancing takes time and costs money. Be clear about why you want to refinance. Decide the type of loan you want, list the required features and do your sums to make sure you won’t be worse off in the long-term.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Options – Fixed or variable rate loan</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">With a variable rate loan, payments increase when interest rates rise. This can affect family budgets and lead to changes in your overall financial circumstances.\r\nRefinancing to a fixed loan can offer protection against rising rates. This can help borrowers who don’t have the cash flow to cover higher loan repayments. Fixing also gives you the ability to budget over the long-term.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Split loans</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">An alternative to fixing your entire home loan is to refinance to a split loan. Split loans let you fix part of your loan and leave the rest on a variable rate. Generally, split loans offer the flexibility and features of variable rate loans whilst offering the certainty of a fixed loan.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Debt Consolidation" tab_id="1426935955516-9"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="grid_16 alpha">\r\n<div class="content-bar sample">\r\n\r\nAre you struggling with high interest costs on your personal debts such as credit cards and personal loans which are affecting your ability to reduce your home loan?\r\n\r\nWe will evaluate your overall finance structure and look at ways of significantly reducing your interest costs by consolidating all of your personal debts into a suitable home loan structure.\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Accelerated Debt Reduction" tab_id="1427106622804-2-8"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]Mauris euismod ante a mauris ultrices malesuada. ivamus tempus gravida elit, eu accumsan dui consectetur sed. Phasellus ipsum risus, sodales ac mauris at, rutrum mattis purus. Aliquam aliquet magna quis justo. Sodales ac mauris at, rutrum mattis purus. Aliquam aliquet magna quis justo.Aliquam aliquet magna quis justo. Sodales ac mauris at, rutrum mattis purus. Aliquam aliquet magna quis justo\r\n\r\nAliquam aliquet magna quis justo.Aliquam aliquet magna quis justo. Sodales ac mauris at, rutrum mattis purus odales ac mauris at, rutrum mattis purus.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Equity Drawing" tab_id="1455583962300-3-0"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]Are you looking for access to the equity in your property?\r\n\r\nThere are a number of acceptable reasons for wanting to do this that Outsource Financial can help you with:\r\n\r\n• Investment purposes;\r\n• Renovations to your home;\r\n• Buying a new car;\r\n• Going on a family holiday;\r\n• Access to funds for upcoming personal expenditure\r\n\r\nWhatever the need be, we are here to help our clients achieve their goals and objectives.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Financial P