ds, and Australian Financial Services Licence holder. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #4d5961;">The Lending Manager has been working in the finance industry for more than 10 years. During that time he has gained valuable experience in structuring finance for a number of clients in residential &amp; commercial lending and equipment leasing. Brendon is accredited with over 30 lenders, holds top professional membership category with the Finance Brokers Association of Australia (FBAA) and is licenced by ASIC to provide credit assistance.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1538-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-28 04:10:21', '2016-02-28 04:10:21', '', 1538, 'http://yesfs.com.au/1538-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
